ABOUT
Self-taught developer building web apps, game concepts, and immersive fiction. I build things that work, worlds that feel real, and code that's intentional. I'm a beginner who actually builds things—bookshelves, games, libraries, stories, and design docs. That puts me ahead of most people stuck on tutorials.

